{"tid":2176507,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官指藏鉗等證據弱 侍應守行為","createTime":"2020-08-27T06:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T06:47:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b52e87b2d572f7ee3dee0309a02931e5e2bfde92","tid":2176507,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T06:38:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/UKWPBCQ3F5AMJBQEANVFMBI2WY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FUKWPBCQ3F5AMJBQEANVFMBI2WY%2F&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk0XpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=55792c14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FUKWPBCQ3F5AMJBQEANVFMBI2WY%2F&h=c813e0f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/UKWPBCQ3F5AMJBQEANVFMBI2WY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n官指藏鉗等證據弱 侍應守行為<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Rug3gSEgGzYYYgupWdAY4WA-r1M=/6720x4480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FZQJ2TSH6FCVVFK6KRGMFKUDNI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRug3gSEgGzYYYgupWdAY4WA-r1M%3D%2F6720x4480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFZQJ2TSH6FCVVFK6KRGMFKUDNI.jpg&h=8fa14bca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年9月在中環舉行的「香港人權與民主祈禱會」中途被警方腰斬。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】網民去年9月在中環舉行「香港人權與民主祈禱會」，惟中途被警方腰斬。有年輕侍應和其他示威者步行往美國駐港總領事館時被警員截查，搜出身藏螺絲批、𠝹刀及剪鉗，被控管有物品意圖損壞財產罪。案件昨再訊，雖侍應獲准以簽保守行為方式結案，但東區法院主任裁判官錢禮明言，控方指控被告管有涉案物品意圖的證據薄弱，強調控方須舉證至毫無合理疑點，香港法律亦是如此規定。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。進行的集會，他就涉案物品的解釋或令人感奇怪及可疑，惟控方的證據頗薄弱。控方只答被告當時在街上管有涉案物品，一旦使用可造成破壞，法庭足以推論。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官再質疑，指被告當時並非穿黑衣，警誡下保持緘默，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女生藏索帶 雷射筆還柙<br />\n<br />\n此外，去年10月6日市民發起反蒙面法遊行，多區爆發警民衝突。警方在旺角區截停18歲女生李芷盈，搜出一包未開封的索帶及一支雷射筆。女生昨承認一項管有攻擊性武器或適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法用途使用罪，九龍城法院主任裁判官嚴舜儀問控方，路障是否由索帶所綑綁，被告逗留時間，又指雖無證據顯示被告曾使用涉案物品，但兩物品皆具風險，下令將被告還柙至下月9日候判。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC807/20、KCCC506/20"},{"pid":"eaa1023349a9ec49e1b6398a498c40dcde1d2580","tid":2176507,"uid":302471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T06:40:43.000Z","msg":"蘇文隆判麵包師傅藏麵包棍六角匙囚9個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4725b2b461392413ddf12905cf4002fd7a9fd667","tid":2176507,"uid":63782,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T06:42:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">強調控方須舉證至毫無合理疑點，香港法律亦是如此規定。</span>"},{"pid":"1e8c5e9f430fc1e2ca98861d2bcd9550797ca64d","tid":2176507,"uid":2377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4725b2b461392413ddf12905cf4002fd7a9fd667","tid":2176507,"uid":63782,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T06:42:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">強調控方須舉證至毫無合理疑點，香港法律亦是如此規定。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T06:43:43.000Z","msg":"個官正常咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a446b8170d59eaaa37c7d0a56d4c0616d28c1b5f","tid":2176507,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4725b2b461392413ddf12905cf4002fd7a9fd667","tid":2176507,"uid":63782,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T06:42:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">強調控方須舉證至毫無合理疑點，香港法律亦是如此規定。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T06:47:17.000Z","msg":"間接提D狗下次老屈都作好D <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}